  {
    "hotel_id": "334356",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/blueboat-hostel-haeundae/hotel/busan-kr.html",
    "name": "Blueboat Hostel Haeundae",
    "detail": "The place was very easy to find and was conveniently near the subway station and bus stops. It was really close Haeundae beach and the traditional Haeundae market, which I highly recommend visitors to go. There were plenty of restaurants and convenience stores around. There was also a massive Daiso and a CGV movie theatre close to the place. However, Haeundae, in general, is quite far from the city centre of Busan, but it shouldn't be a problem since transportation (buses and subways) are really accessible from the guesthouse. The place is well maintained and the facilities available are modern. I love the interior of the place, it's very welcoming and pleasing. What you see on the pictures is what you get in real life. However, the bathroom stalls were quite unusual for me since the divider was only a semi-see-through glass, but it wasn't a big deal since I took showers when no one was around. Breakfast was included in our stay which was a massive plus. You need to be quick though especially if there are lots of other guests staying; the food could run out. The staff members were really nice and friendly. They were always willing to help us out. Overall, the guesthouse was a really good value for the price we paid. We enjoyed our stay in Busan and had an enjoyable stay at the guesthouse for 5 nights. I would recommend this place to anyone who wants to stay near Haeundae beach and is looking for an excellent bargain!",
